snippet.title: Diana and Minnie Mouse Birthday
snippet.description:
Today is Minnie Mouse's birthday. Diana buys a dress as a gift for Minnie, but keeps it for herself. Then Diana buys new gifts - toys Minnie Mouse. But she also needed these toys!...
